| Technical Integration Risk | API incompatibility with legacy TMS; latency under peak volume; model drift; scalability constraints during Prime Day/holidays; third-party data provider dependencies. | Full architecture and API compatibility review as pre-close condition; integration and load testing at simulated peak volume; continuous AI model monitoring with drift detection alerts; third-party vendor SLAs; fallback routing engine at all stations. |
